  "prompt": "Should I send a Facebook friend request to ex bf?",
  "response": "Deciding whether to send a Facebook friend request to an ex-boyfriend depends on several factors:\n\n1. **Current Feelings**: Are you over the relationship? If you still have strong feelings, it might be better to hold off.\n\n2. **Reasons for the Request**: Consider why you want to connect. Is it for closure, friendship, or curiosity? Be clear about your intentions.\n\n3. **Past Relationship Dynamics**: How did the relationship end? If it was amicable, a friendship could be possible. If it ended on bad terms, it might be best to avoid contact.\n\n4. **Mutual Friends**: If you have many mutual friends and it feels awkward not being connected, it might be worth considering.\n\n5. **Your Current Situation**: Are you in a new relationship? If so, consider how your partner might feel about the request.\n\nUltimately, trust your instincts and think about what\u2019s best for your emotional well-being.",
